// Get UUIDs from lands collection and join them with commas
const uuids = collections['f45a35d7-4c2e-4c9d-b34e-2fbe243b16c6']?.data?.map(land => land.uuid).join(',');

// Create iframe HTML string with dynamic parcelId parameter
return `<iframe
  src="https://backend.beforbuild.com/webhook/mappy?parcelId=${uuids}"
  width="100%"
  height="100%"
  style="border: none;"
  allowfullscreen="true"
  loading="lazy"
  referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
  title="Carte cadastrale de France"
>
</iframe>`;
